creator: shelves
descriptionHtml:
We are a platform that aims to gather all top-tier Saudi brands under one roof, to enhance the user's experience and to fill the gap between the local supply and demand with a goal to be the largest Saudi online marketplace

Our website operates a digital marketplace connecting brands, and consumers. Our platform uses data and artificial intelligence That automates decision making through the application of machine learning to guide merchandising, targeting, curation and feedback. We also offers supply chain monitoring for partners and manage logistics.
